This is a Chrome extension that works with Salesforce.com.

If you are on a Salesforce.com record page, you can click the scissors icon to clip the Id to your clipboard. The icon turns green when you successfully clip the Id.

To install:

1. Download the source to your computer
2. Go to Chrome
3. Window > Extensions
4. Click the + next to Developer Mode
5. Load unpacked extension
6. Browse to the downloaded directory

Source code is on github:

https://github.com/gokubi/Salesforce-Id-Clipper-Chrome-Extension